      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Fishystuff Operator Overview\nUse this as the first-stop dashboard for beta or production traffic.\n\n- `Sessions Started` shows whether people are actively entering the site.\n- `Frontend Error Signals`, `Page Ready`, and `Map Ready` surface user-facing regressions.\n- Trace rate and latency panels show which service or operation is drifting.\n- The logs panel stays focused on warning and error signals for fast triage.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
